Then defend me.

1007
01:24:03.247 --> 01:24:06.459
I won't let my record be tainted
on my last day.

1008
01:24:09.170 --> 01:24:12.173
From now on.
we'll do things my way.

1009
01:24:12.673 --> 01:24:15.843
