1081
01:28:26.510 --> 01:28:29.430
But Laura had already crossed
the point of no return.

1082
01:28:30.597 --> 01:28:34.518
And when she told you her plan.
you lost your head.

1083
01:28:42.359 --> 01:28:44.486
When you got her
programmed message.

1084
