1102
01:30:38.475 --> 01:30:41.562
If Laura was going to tell them
the truth. why not call the police?

1103
01:30:41.812 --> 01:30:43.605
They know you'll never
incriminate yourself

1104
01:30:43.772 --> 01:30:46.817
